node.text: This process was insane! I started trying to organize this all when I was 8 months pregnant but I noticed I was doing too much when my feet started swelling like giant tortas 😂 So @riorganize came in and took over and WOW! This organization is on another level. It’s been a long time now and it’s still stays organized because of how effective it was done! I uploaded a whole YouTube video going through it all in detail and if you like to see the process check her page out as well! @riorganize 🙌🏽 her page is so satisfying and I get so many ideas over there. A must follow for sure.
